度及流通量较大的二手屋苑。 尽管如此，多名业内人士在接受《每日经济新闻》记者采访时表示，目前虽然「撤辣」效应在逐渐减弱，5 月一手成交量约 1400 宗，较「撤辣」后 3 月的逾 4000 宗回落，但整体来看，成交量仍高于 2021 年旺市时平均值，交投仍然活跃。香港楼市「撤辣」三个月：中介购房群快没人说话了，内地客户买走大量新盘 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-756326da81730810118ea0c203b7cd72_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658172341"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/aaYvpHB7rFdEAMaCTEwODUzODU4MCCUw4GzBjAAOERAFXIJNjU4MTcyMzQxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1717720772.364114", "card_id": "Q_658008107", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 151}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么是「傲慢」？你认为「读书越多越傲慢，还是读书越少越傲慢」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-87e164b99419185ca15a62c482e377c4_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658008107"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/aaYvpHB7rFdEAMaCTEwODUwMjAwMyDStfeyBjAAON8BQBZyCTY1ODAwODEwN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1717720772.364394", "card_id": "Q_603615846", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "袁崇焕和皇太极的军事才能哪个更强？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a81fbe80cd5b6a78ef35a352f441d282_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603615846"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/aaYvpHB7rFdEAMaCDk2NDE3Mjg5IKHq0KMGMAA4VUAXcgk2MDM2MTU4NDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZ